{"tid":671792,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"葵聯村空中花園唔係公共空間？","createTime":"2018-05-20T12:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T12:33:38.000Z","uid":59298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f94f904d2ed78e79f77d37079a63ae81debea0b3","tid":671792,"uid":59298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:09:40.000Z","msg":"小弟今日見咁好天，雖然好撚熱，就去搵地方影下相 - 葵盛西邨同葵聯邨，會一會佢個空中花園<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出發之前做咗research, 葵聯邨嘅空中花園係公共空間，開放俾一般民眾嘅<br />\n「葵聯邨第二期，工程項目名稱葵盛圍公屋發展計劃......[red]此通道及空中花園，為公共空間，免費開放予公眾使用，惠及附近居民。［/red]」<br />\n<br />\n到差唔多六點半嘅時候，我到咗葵聯邨，同保安姐姐講我先登記，請求上去空中花園，再放低身份證。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n保安姐姐話要call控制室先，之後我等咗10分鐘，控制室話唔得。<span style=\"font-size: large;\">[red]我去同控制室討論，貴屋邨嘅空中花園係公共空間，一般民眾係有權先登記後進入。<br />\n佢叫我聽日九點打俾佢老總同佢講。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ［/red]</span><br />\n最後我見到開始燒天，狗衝翻葵盛西邨搵位影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">唔知係因為保安問題，定係人流少，會令到一個公共空間變成非公共空間。我地應唔應該捍衛應有嘅權利，定係唔好煩鳩佢地？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［size=2]如果已經確定唔係公共空間，細力屌唔該[/size=2]<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2d59002516784bbc9a9ce89e20420b1c44f18a","tid":671792,"uid":59298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:10:42.000Z","msg":"自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHTML做乜唔work"},{"pid":"3a52ceda34f2519cd1a58864a08d9e348167fda6","tid":671792,"uid":179783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:18:13.000Z","msg":"錯台呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546573be223f871a063283bb274f19804d7cfacf","tid":671792,"uid":59298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a52ceda34f2519cd1a58864a08d9e348167fda6","tid":671792,"uid":179783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:18:13.000Z","msg":"錯台呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d526cf1cc8dd34717acdb13b58259de4b69fb1","tid":671792,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> なに？"}]}